text: Take This to Your Grave is the second studio album by rock band Fall Out Boy. The album was released 2003. Credits are Patrick Stump, Pete Wentz, Joe Trohman, and Andy Hurley. == Tracklisting == 1\. "Tell That Mick He Just Made My List of Things to Do Today" 2\. "Dead on Arrival" 3\.
